# 🚀 ESP32 IR Sensor Dashboard

## 📌 Overview

This project is a real-time object detection system using **ESP32 + IR Sensor** with a web-based dashboard.

The system detects objects and updates status live on a browser.

---

## ⚙️ Features

* 🔥 Real-time object detection
* 🌐 Web dashboard (ESP32 hosted)
* 📡 Wireless monitoring (WiFi)
* 💡 LED indication

---

## 🛠️ Hardware Used

* ESP32
* IR Sensor Module
* Jumper wires
* Laptop / Power supply

